"1  dozen small, shucked oysters, drained (1/2 pint)","1/4 cup flour","1  egg, lightly beaten","3/4 cup Japanese breadcrumbs*","1/4 cup butter, divided","2  shallots, minced","2  (3.2-ounce) packages shiitake mushrooms, stems removed, sliced","1/2 cup dry sherry","1 cup whipping cream","3 cups coarsely shredded cooked turkey (white and dark meat)","2 tablespoons chopped fresh tarragon","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground pepper","3  large croissants (about 2 ounces each), split and toasted","  Garnishes: tarragon sprigs, lemon wedges"